{
  "stem": "14091.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided, since I was smaller and younger, and I didn't weigh that much, that I would try to crawl first.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did crawl out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found a stem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I stood on that stem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I gave a hand to my sister, Celia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow, I-- I took her out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we looked absolutely horrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to clean ourselves of the black little leeches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we start walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got out of the swamp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we start walking towards dry land.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, we saw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We came to the edge of the woods, and we saw there a farm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when we start walking towards the farm, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some kind of miracle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We saw my sister running out of that house and screaming to us, my sister Chaya.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was there with my aunt screaming to us and showing us with her arm that we should hide.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We should run.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We should go away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But police was in this house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And by her running out, they shot her on the spot and also my aunt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were hiding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We laid down in the woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We hid there, and we saw it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But she still had the-- when she saw us, apparently, I don't know how she managed to show us that we shouldn't go closer there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We laid there in the woods until it got really dark.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then, we discuss what we should do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Celia remembered that not very far from there, it was a farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The name was Lapuszyno.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there lived a family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The name was Bielewicz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were very friendly with the family.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
